  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个设备数据查询的流程图。场景是外部系统通过API获取设备信息，核心是要体现过滤条件的传递和实际数据获取的分离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为前端有个API Client发起请求，后端需要DeviceController来接收。过滤条件是用DeviceFilterInput这个对象来封装吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DeviceFilterInput专门承载过滤参数。另外关键一点是Controller自己不查数据，要委派给DeviceDataFetcher，这样职责更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那DeviceDataFetcher直接连数据源？我打算画一条线到DataSource，标注为\"applies filters\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。DataFetcher把过滤条件应用到Device Data Source上，然后拿到结果返回给Controller。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先画出主干：API Client发送filter input到DeviceController，Controller使用DeviceFilterInput，然后委派给DeviceDataFetcher。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，API Client到Controller的箭头标注，我觉得用\"sends filter input\"更准确，不是简单的调用关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下标注。另外检查下：DeviceDataFetcher查完数据后，需要把结果返回给DeviceController，这条线不能漏。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，返回结果的标注用\"returns results\"。最后Controller要响应API Client，标注\"responds\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController",
